      • StreamingShapeWriter

        public StreamingShapeWriter(String workingDir,
                            boolean shapeIndex,
                            List<String> skipAttributeNames)
                     throws IOException
        Constructor for creating a StreamingShapeWriter. The writer wil stream the features to different shapefiles in the given working dir.
        Parameters:
        workingDir - The working dir where the shape writer is going to write the shape files
        shapeIndex - If true a index wil be created on the shape files.
        skipAttributeNames - a list of attribute names that needs to be skipped (default only boundedBy)
        Throws:
        IOException
